title: David Bowie - 2002-10-17 Jimmys Bronx Cafe New York City
description:
Another very nice David Bowie recording. Check my account for more Bowie stuff.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


DAVID BOWIE

NEW YORK, NY (USA)
OCTOBER 17, 2002
FROM THE COLLECTION OF SMORES
KRW&CO TRANSFER/SMORES UPLOAD # 402

LINEAGE AUDIENCE DAT MASTER(48KHZ)>DAT CLONE>SONY PCM R-300 DAT>FIBER OPTIC>CREATIVE SOUNDBLASTER X-FI HD MODEL #SB1240

This show is another from the collection of "Smores" who is working to get many of his old tapes transferred and uploaded for others to enjoy. 
Some of these shows are seeing the light of day after all of these years- some for the first time since they were taped!
